Esso Singapore Pte Ltd said it raisedpump prices of petrol from today.    New prices for 0.15 gm lead grades are 97.0 cents/litre for97 octane and 90.8 cents for 95 octane.    Other Singapore oil companies announced yesterday that theywould revise their pump prices effective today.    Shell Eastern Petroleum Pte Ltd, Mobil Oil Singapore PteLtd, Caltex Asia Ltd, Singapore Petroleum Co Pte Ltd and BPSingapore Pte Ltd are pricing 97 octane at 96.8 cents. Shell,Mobil and Caltex are pricing 92 octane at 90.2 cents, and SPCand BP at 90.6 cents. REUTER&#3;